{"word":"φθόρος","slug":"φθόρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φθόρος</b></el> <el>(φθόρος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:φθορά'><el>φθορά</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><el>ἴτ' ἐς φθόρον  φθείρεσθε</el> (<a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:φθείρω'><el>φθείρω</el></a> II. 1) a common form of cursing, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>οὐκ ἐς φθόρον</el>; <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>ὄλεθρος</el>, <i>a pestilent fellow</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}